{"tier":3,"question":"What is 'Maillard reaction' temperature range?","answer":"Above about 140-165°C (280-330°F)","choices":["Around 100°C (boiling point)","Above about 140-165°C (280-330°F)","Above 200°C only","Between 60-80°C"]},
